According to the research by the [[Aberdeen Group]], organizations with the most highly agile BI implementations are more likely to have processes in place for ensuring that business needs are being met.{{r|Getting a fast start with agile BI development}}  Success of Agile BI implementation also heavily depends on end user participation and "frequent collaboration between IT and the business."{{r|Getting a fast start with agile BI development}}
